<p><b>What is the 5th edition of DnD?</b> Dungeons & Dragons 5th edition is an edition of the Dungeons & Dragons tabletop roleplaying game rules first published by Wizards of the Coast in 2014. As of 2024, it is the most recent edition of the Dungeons & Dragons rules.</p>
